.subsubsection Patient Photo

The patient photo is displayed at the top left hand side of the clinical screen. If not photo exists then a blank place-holder is shown: 

.image clinical/gui/maintoolbar/patient_photo_blank.png

To add a photo you have two options

.item Access the Patients module from the main sidebar menu see 
.xref Adding a Photograph
.item Right mouse click over the photograph in the clinical section:

.image clinical/gui/maintoolbar/patient_photo.png

A popup menu will give you options for adding, saving, deleting an existing photo.